#~ "15% de les processades)\n"
#~ " canvia el justificat\n"
#~ " i/o la font           :  364 ( 7% del total; 11% de les no ignorades; "
#~ "13% de les processades)\n"
#~ "\n"

# type: verbatim
#~ msgid ""
#~ " undetected problems:   68 ( 1% of all;  2% of unignored;  2% of "
#~ "processed)\n"
#~ "\n"
